{"tid":645942,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(片+圖)終於有隻神獸走左入黎,嗡嗡嗡","createTime":"2018-04-28T15:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:38:03.000Z","uid":119688,"like":37,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"74021b05fa40cbb7b42244baf9e63e07a027cf64","tid":645942,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:19:46.000Z","msg":"本身玩緊勁舞團<br />\n無啦啦見佢係地下周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係比佢嚇死 衰鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://vimple.co/712ff241e54148078d8b04736ff7bdb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvimple.co%2F712ff241e54148078d8b04736ff7bdb5&d=RAoqGISUx%2BsfqzXPWYbO3Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c041753d\" target=\"_blank\">vimple.co/712ff241e54148078d8b04736ff7bdb5</a><br />\n點知比佢un下un下又無事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迫我出招泰山壓頂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/231049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F231049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=057d3dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見佢求生力幾強,<br />\n點壓都比佢走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://vimple.co/2baef1fc97e644d1bdfd7a71daf3675a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvimple.co%2F2baef1fc97e644d1bdfd7a71daf3675a&d=RAoqGISUx%2BsfqzXPWYbO3Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=dfcb69cb\" target=\"_blank\">vimple.co/2baef1fc97e644d1bdfd7a71daf3675a</a><br />\n<br />\n於是比佢打動左,打算養大佢<br />\n當佢係仔,我仲諗到整間屋仔比佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/231923_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F231923_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4133dbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲未改名 聽日諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9e1b26b509f5178211cb79263a1ac1346afb07","tid":645942,"uid":138552,"like":8,"dislike":258,"score":-250,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d5b39098b8de3605c2d45dea3bc7a50f648c25d","tid":645942,"uid":54176,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"小心佢吹雞"},{"pid":"31a87d3cdd7b60f898be96958fcc96d5a4ff999a","tid":645942,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d5b39098b8de3605c2d45dea3bc7a50f648c25d","tid":645942,"uid":54176,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"小心佢吹雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:22:23.000Z","msg":"而且都驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022ecfea4578899359cba1f5aae14f72896ea398","tid":645942,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"上面D片 整走url就睇到<br />\n手機上傳唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0ba7a2a091e3c030a0b847dbadea58685587bd","tid":645942,"uid":35129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"有無教佢叫椰汁炸豬扒~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c4ed4c9a74f664bb59eb57fd466b31a8c824b2","tid":645942,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ba0ba7a2a091e3c030a0b847dbadea58685587bd","tid":645942,"uid":35129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"scor